、藍白兩種顏色可供選擇，該機採用 Symbian OS v9.4 操作系統，基於 S60 5th Edition 平台。X6 的機身厚度只有 13.8mm，相比前作 N97、5800 XpressMusic 都要薄很多，相比 iPhone 還是略厚。另外，X6 能連續播放音樂達 35 小時，與 iPhone 相當。<br />\n<br />\n定位高端市場的 X6，配備 500 萬像素的「卡爾‧蔡司」自動對焦攝頭以及雙 LED 閃光燈，這一點遠勝於 iPhone。X6 有效工作頻率為 433MHz 的中央處理器，以及 32GB 機身存儲空間，與 iPhone 旗鼓相當。不過 X6 省略了 micro SD（T-Flash）存儲卡插槽，同時 1600 萬色、360 x 640 解像度 TFT 觸控螢幕，其面積由 3.5 吋降為 3.2 吋。<br />\n<br />\n另外，X6 還預裝 Ovi 商店，並支援 Come With Music 服務。Ovi 商店是 Nokia 重點打造的商店軟件，儘管目前還比不上 Apple 的 App Store，但是將來全面的 Ovi 服務，將有機會全面超越 App Store。</blockquote><br />\n今時今日睇返好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢篇已成經典，上兩登嘅人，一定要識"},{"pid":"843596af373191baf590a8e0087abfebb4a1c77b","tid":358643,"uid":134382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npro2 同g3都燒底板"},{"pid":"27ed058e5a84d63e322662b5cac47a9cd7aa20af","tid":358643,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:31:49.000Z","msg":"底板不了"},{"pid":"337c1df2435cdc97b7409c899d80fe1ed9ea18b1","tid":358643,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果我有錢一定買iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\niPhone 邊個model有<br />\n雙<br />\n卡？"},{"pid":"de3ba33d27977a53b7126610a498feef6a07df04","tid":358643,"uid":62658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"LG 轉左去HTC <br />\n返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c449708be1c36dac02438c6efee1a29ccef6e5","tid":358643,"uid":91398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影相一開始係靚既<br />\n但用得幾個月<br />\nd色真係差左又矇左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都覺o的機用耐o左影相會無咁靚<br />\n有時諗究竟係咪心理作用"},{"pid":"ee55d011d3b8217a7e301cc90caa5c89133bc85a","tid":358643,"uid":1085,"like"